# itemName

**Type Property**

A key that specifies the name of the accessory panel setting.

## Declaration

```swift
static let itemName: NSPrintPanel.AccessorySummaryKey
```

## Discussion

The corresponding value should be an [doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/Foundation/NSString] object.

## Summary Keys

- **itemDescription**: A key that identfies the current value of the accessory panel setting.
